desc: Specialists in natural feeds for working, sporting and pet dogs. Large selection of high quality raw feeds, meats and minces. Approved suppliers and distributers of CSJ Dog Food for North West England. Advice on all aspects of canine diet and feeding. UK wide delivery service.

layout.text:
We promise to treat your dogs with the same care as we would our own. We believe that great condition starts with great food! Our carefully chosen range includes performance feeds for working, sporting and competing dogs, and a fantastic selection of high quality raw meats and minces for raw fed dogs.
* obedience * agility * flyball * search and rescue * racing sled dogs * protection dogs * detection dogs * gun dogs * herding dogs * canicross*
